  "text": "The error decomposition (4.3) is fairly common in analyzing standard online learning algorithm [CITATION_1] . The term S 1 (t) 2 ρ is related to an initial error, which is deterministic and will be estimated in the next section. The term E {z j ,v j } t j=1 [ S 2 (t) 2 ρ ] is a sample error depending on the sample, which will be estimated in Section 6.",
